snippet.title: Key Hunters - SAGE 2019 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Key Hunters has finally returned!

Sonic & Knuckles: Key Hunters is a Sonic Fangame that tackles on some odd concepts and tries to take a new spin on it. Its based on the Emerald Hunting Stages from Sonic Adventure 1 & 2, Sonic Labyrinth & Sonic Mania. 

Voice Actors:
Sonic & Knuckles - Landy
Mighty - TrevZed

Animated by EnderElectrics

For new demo's and updates on Key Hunters, visit the website:
https://sites.google.com/view/sonic-project-twisted/homepage
